      "content": "it's been like this for about 20 mins now. it's just super intense. i've had migraines before and they're bad but this feels different, just more sudden. u think i should just take some extra ibuprofen and wait it out? i really don't want to sit in an ER for 6 hours if it's just a migraine flare up.",
